Package: ABwaterwells
Type: Package
Title: Retrieval and Analysis of the Alberta Water Well Information Database
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Steven Pawley
Maintainer: Steven Pawley <dr.stevenpawley@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a set of tools for obtaining water well data from the
    Alberta Environment and Protected Areas (AEPA) OData service and performing
    geological and hydrogeological analyses.
